						               													<description>From the Malifaux Tactica Wiki:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A powerful model that uses Burning Tokens to power its spells, abilities and attacks. It can be the heavy hitter many crews lack, and even though expensive, you are getting a massive piece for only 9 (or 10) SS.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Rail Golem works well with models that can put Burning Tokens on it, but it is self sufficient enough to work with any crew.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Rail Golem has very significant offensive abilities. Its melee weapon has a good reach, is Paired, and causes grievous damage, and it can use Burning Tokens to get positive twists to attack or damage, or an extra melee attack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The main &amp;quot;trick&amp;quot; with the Rail Golem is to balance out how it accumulates and uses Burning Tokens. Often, you will need to balance between increasing attacks in a short-term way (by increasing attacks and damage flips, or getting an extra attack), healing up (by burning all tokens for 1 Wd of healing each), or saving them up to Reactivate (which costs 5 tokens, but can be very powerful.)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
